<item>
            <title>[SOLR-11199] Support OR queries in the Payload Score Parser </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-11199</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;PayloadScoreQParserPlugin always creates a SpanNearQuery. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In my use-case I want to be able to do an OR query and then use a sum function to sum up all the scores.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So if the PayloadScoreQParserPlugin supported an operator param which could be used to pick between phrase searches ( the default currently ) OR and ANDs &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13092572">SOLR-11199</key>
            <summary>Support OR queries in the Payload Score Parser </summary>
